{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/47907", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/47907/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/47907/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/47907/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/47907", "id": 293197514, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUyOTMxOTc1MTQ=", "number": 47907, "title": "\"cannot assign to `...` because it is borrowed\" error can be circumvent in pattern-matching", "user": {"login": "thierry-martinez", "id": 1289010, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEyODkwMTA=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1289010?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez", "html_url": "https://github.com/thierry-martinez", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2018-01-31T15:22:00Z", "updated_at": "2018-01-31T21:34:38Z", "closed_at": "2018-01-31T21:34:38Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "The following code is accepted by the compiler (tested with rustc 1.23 and rustc 1.24.0-beta.8):\r\n\r\n```\r\nfn main() {\r\n    let mut a = 0;\r\n    let mut b = 1;\r\n    let mut ref_a = &mut a;\r\n    let (ref mut ref_ref_a, ()) = (ref_a, ());\r\n    ref_a = &mut b;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nHowever, assigning to `ref_a` should not be allowed while `ref_a` is borrowed by `ref_ref_a`. Indeed, the following code, which looks equivalent to the code above, is rejected by the compiler:\r\n\r\n```\r\nfn main() {\r\n    let mut a = 0;\r\n    let mut b = 1;\r\n    let mut ref_a = &mut a;\r\n    let ref mut ref_ref_a = ref_a;\r\n    ref_a = &mut b;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\nerror[E0506]: cannot assign to `ref_a` because it is borrowed\r\n --> src/main.rs:6:5\r\n  |\r\n5 |     let ref mut ref_ref_a = ref_a;\r\n  |         ----------------- borrow of `ref_a` occurs here\r\n6 |     ref_a = &mut b;\r\n  |     ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ assignment to borrowed `ref_a` occurs here\r\n```", "closed_by": {"login": "thierry-martinez", "id": 1289010, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEyODkwMTA=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1289010?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez", "html_url": "https://github.com/thierry-martinez", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thierry-martinez/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/47907/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/47907/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}